question.text: "For 4D, if I bet RM 1\r\nand it hits second place\r\nhow much does it pay?"

languages.ms: "4d klau bet rm 1\r\nklau Naik no 2\r\nberapa bayar"

detailed.en:
"BOX

If the number has 24 permutations

Buy BOX RM 1 x 24 = RM 24 to pay
One number RM 1

BOX = x

1234 = 24 sets
1134 = 12 sets
1133 = 6 sets
1113 = 4 sets

------------------------------

IBOX

If the number has 24 permutations

Buy IBOX for RM 1 only to get 24 number sets
24 ÷ RM 1 = RM 0.04 per number

IBOX = ÷

1234 = 24 sets
1134 = 12 sets
1133 = 6 sets
1113 = 4 sets"
detailed.ms:
"BOX

Jika Nombor Pusingan 24 kali

Beli BOX rm1 x 24 =rm24 Kena Bayar
Satu Nombor Rm1

BOX = x

1234 =24 Pasang
1134 =12 Pasang
1133 =6 Pasang
1113 =4 Pasang

------------------------------

IBOX

Jika Nombor Pusingan 24 kali

Beli IBOX Bayar RM1 Saja Boleh Dapat 24 Pasang Nombor
24 ÷ RM1 ＝ Rm0.04 Satu Nombor

IBOX = ÷

1234 =24 Pasang
1134 =12 Pasang
1133 =6 Pasang
1113 =4 Pasang"

如果號碼有24種組合
